---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  locale="en"
  title="About | jhle0"
  description="About jhle0"
  canonicalPath="/en/about"
>
  <section class="about-page">
    <aside class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="about-sidebar-panel surface-card">
        <div class="about-profile-card">
          <img
            class="about-profile-image"
            src="/images/profile/profile.jpg"
            alt="Profile photo of Lee Jeonghyeon"
          />
          <div>
            <p class="about-profile-kicker">Developer archive</p>
            <h2>Lee Jeonghyeon</h2>
            <p>A developer growing through CS, AI, and writing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-fact-list">
          <section class="about-fact-item">
            <h3>Location</h3>
            <p>South Korea</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-fact-item">
            <h3>Current</h3>
            <p>Military service · Studying CS and AI</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-fact-item">
            <h3>Direction</h3>
            <p>
              I want to build a strong foundation in CS, understand machine
              learning and deep learning properly, explore multimodal and
              embodied AI in depth, and eventually grow toward Physical AI.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="about-tech-stack">
          <div class="about-tech-intro">
            <h3>Technologies</h3>
          </div>

          <section class="about-tech-group">
            <h4>Languages</h4>
            <ul class="about-tech-grid tone-sand">
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Python</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">C / C++</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Dart</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">JavaScript</span></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-tech-group">
            <h4>Frameworks & Libraries</h4>
            <ul class="about-tech-grid tone-blue">
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">React</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Flutter</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Django</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Astro</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">FastAPI</span></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-tech-group">
            <h4>Tools / Infra</h4>
            <ul class="about-tech-grid tone-green">
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">GitHub</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Docker</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Linux</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Vercel</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Google Cloud</span></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-tech-group">
            <h4>AI / Data</h4>
            <ul class="about-tech-grid tone-mint">
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">PyTorch</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">NumPy</span></li>
              <li><span class="about-tech-chip">Pandas</span></li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="about-main">
      <section class="page-intro">
        <p class="eyebrow">About me</p>
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p class="intro-copy">
          Hello. I am Lee Jeonghyeon, a developer who records what he studies
          and builds. I am currently serving in the military while steadily
          studying CS fundamentals and AI-related topics.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rather than reading a concept once and moving on, I care more about
          reorganizing it in my own words, implementing it myself, and leaving
          a clear record behind. This site is the space where I collect study
          notes, project logs, and thoughts from the process.
        </p>
        <p>
          In the long run, I want to properly understand machine learning and
          deep learning on top of strong CS fundamentals, focus on multimodal
          and embodied AI, and continue extending that direction toward
          Physical AI.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section-block">
        <h2>Values & Philosophy</h2>
        <div class="info-card-grid">
          <article class="info-card surface-card">
            <h3>Endure to the end</h3>
            <p>
              I do not give up easily once I have chosen a direction. Even if
              my pace slows down in the middle, I believe the ability to keep
              going matters most in the end.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card surface-card">
            <h3>Deep focus</h3>
            <p>
              When I start something, I value diving deep and making it my own
              more than touching many things superficially.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card surface-card">
            <h3>Grow through systems</h3>
            <p>
              I prefer building structures and routines that make consistency
              possible instead of relying only on willpower. I believe growth
              lasts longer when it happens inside systems of notes, review, and
              reflection.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="info-card surface-card">
            <h3>Small steps compound</h3>
            <p>
              I believe small growth accumulated every day eventually creates a
              big difference. The quiet repetition of ordinary days is what
              takes me where I want to go.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-block">
        <h2>Beyond Work</h2>
        <div class="interest-grid">
          <article class="interest-card surface-card">
            <h3>Scuba Diving</h3>
            <p>
              I hold an open-water scuba diving license. I enjoy it as a hobby
              because it lets me immerse myself in a completely different
              environment outside work and study.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="interest-card surface-card">
            <h3>Golf</h3>
            <p>
              I am still learning, but I enjoy the process of slowly refining
              posture, rhythm, and consistency, so it is a hobby I want to keep
              growing with personally.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-block">
        <h2>Links</h2>
        <ul class="inline-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/jhle0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              GitHub
            </a>
          </li>
          <li><a href="mailto:dumiso04@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/blog">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/projects">Projects</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/now">Now</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
